Package MOBLIMA

Class PriceType

java.lang.Object
MOBLIMA.PriceType
public class PriceType extends Object
Represents base prices that can be included in the cost of a ticket Prices are broken down into the type of movie, type and date of screening, age of moviegoer, and GST
